snippet.title: Conduct THIS! Trains of the Month Update
snippet.description:
We're excited to announce a big new update for our beloved mobile game Conduct THIS!

Our Commuter Pass players will now be able to earn a brand new train every single month!

Play the game on Google Play (https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=co.northplay.ConductTHIS)

And the App Store (https://apps.apple.com/app/apple-store/id1151455384)
